text:
Minor improvements to javadoc in the org.apache.catalina package.
Removed unused imports in the org.apache.catalina package.

Unused imports have been removed from all currently supported code bases.

The Cluster implementation has been re-written since 4.1.x so that part of the patch cannot easily be applied.
